sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Grid
    participant Cell
    participant Flag
    participant Mimic

    Player->>Grid: Move (WASD/Arrows)
    Grid->>Cell: Get tile under player
    Player->>Flag: Walk over flag
    Flag-->>Player: Add to inventory (max 2)

    Player->>Cell: Look at number (no reveal)
    Cell-->>Player: Show current number

    Mimic->>Cell: Change one number (only after reveals)